p.span: We are business, government and civic leaders working together to foster growth, positive development and improve the quality of life for all citizens in the Floyd County area.

div.p: To facilitate new business, assist existing business growth and aid county community leaders in efforts for economic development.
We are business, government and civic leaders working together to foster growth, positive development and improve the quality of life for all citizens in the Floyd County area.

h3.span: Why join the Floyd County Chamber of Commerce?

div.p: Chamber membership provides numerous opportunities to grow and strengthen your business. With community support, the Chamber is able to build programs to represent the interests of business to government, support the community, encourage a strong local economy, provide marketing opportunities, advocate political action and promote the development of community leaders.

The Floyd County Chamber of Commerce Board of Directors and staff strive to deliver services for businesses both small and large. We rely on business support and membership to create a positive and successful business environment in Floyd County.
